yplatz), auf dem Bauernmarkt im Hessenpark, dem Laurentiusmarkt in Usingen und zahlreichen anderen Märkten im Usingen Land.\nNe­ben dem Hof­la­den gibt es auf dem Hof noch 30 Pen­si­onsp­fer­de­bo­xen und ei­nen Reit­platz. Die Pfer­de­pen­si­on bie­tet so­wohl im Som­mer als auch im Win­ter Platz für zahl­rei­che Vier­bei­ner. Zusätzlich finden auf dem Talhof regelmäßig Seminare zur traditionellen handwerklichen Herstellung von Hofkäse sowie Sensenkurse statt.","foundedAtYear":2017,"foundedAtMonth":3,"maximumMembers":30,"additionalProductInformation":"","participation":"Mithilfe im Gewächshaus und auf dem Acker. Oder in allen Belangen die Solawi betreffend","actsEcological":false,"economicalBehavior":"Wir sind nicht bio-zertifiziert. Die Solawi hat sich allerdings dazu entschlossen biologisch zu arbeiten","createdAt":"2020-03-24T12:16:25.305Z","updatedAt":null,"country":"DEU","state":"Hessen","postalcode":"61250","depots":{"type":"FeatureCollection","features":[]},"products":[{"id":"1","category":"vegetable_products","name":"vegetables","type":"Product","link":"/products/1"},{"id":"2","category":"vegetable_products","name":"fruits","type":"Product","link":"/products/2"},{"id":"6","category":"vegetable_products","name":"spices","type":"Product","link":"/products/6"},{"id":"7","category":"animal_products","name":"eggs","type":"Product","link":"/products/7"},{"id":"8","category":"animal_products","name":"meat","type":"Product","link":"/products/8"},{"id":"10","category":"animal_products","name":"milk","type":"Product","link":"/products/10"},{"id":"11","category":"animal_products","name":"dairy","type":"Product","link":"/products/11"},{"id":"13","category":"animal_products","name":"honey","type":"Product","link":"/products/13"},{"id":"14","category":"beverages","name":"juice","type":"Product","link":"/products/14"}],"badges":[{"id":"1","name":"Netzwerk Solidarische Landwirtschaft e.V.","category":"associations","url":"https://www.solidarische-landwirtschaft.org/","logo